List all objects in a package's user-cache pins board

Source: R/pkgpins.gen.R
ls_cache.Rd

Lists all object ids belonging to a pkg's user-cache pins board, together with some metadata (see cache_obj() for details).

ls_cache(board)

Arguments

board

Package's user-cache pins board.

Value

A tibble.
